articles.author: Madison Hoff
articles.title: There's no jobs report. Here's what six recent analyses show instead. - Business Insider
articles.description: The Bureau of Labor Statistics won't be publishing the October jobs report on Friday. LinkedIn, Bank of America, and more crunched their own numbers.
articles.content:
Economists, journalists, and investors won't be waiting by their laptops this morning for a new jobs report.
It's the second month without this data release. The agency isn't releasing most reports … [+6443 chars]
